{
    "title": "Ainda é tempo de ser feliz",
    "artist": "Zeca Pagodinho",
    "composer": "Arlindo Cruz",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/C\">D/C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm9\">Bm9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7(9-)\">E7(9-)</span>\r\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D4(9)\">D4(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M\">G7M</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7\">Db7</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Solo]\r</span>\n\r\n\n\r\n\n\r\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm6\">Cm6</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm6/F\">Dm6/F</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7(4)\">E7(4)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Me cansei de ficar mudo sem tentar,       sem falar\r</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm6\">Cm6</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(13)\">B7(13)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(13-)\">B7(13-)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7(9-)\">E7(9-)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas não posso deixar tudo como está  Como está você?\r</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm6\">Cm6</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tô vivendo por viver, tô cansada de chorar\r</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7(4)\">E7(4)</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não sei mais o que fazer, você tem que me ajudar\r</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(13-)\">B7(13-)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7(9)\">Em7(9)</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tá difícil esquecer, impossível não lembrar vocêêê\r</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7(13)\">G7(13)</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E você como está?\r</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#m7(5-)\">C#m7(5-)</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com o fim do nosso amor, eu também tô por aí\r</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7(5-)\">Bm7(5-)</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E9-\">E9-</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu não sei pra onde vou, tantas noites sem dormir\r</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(13)\">D7(13)</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M\">G7M</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Alivia minha dor, e me faça por favor   sorrir\r</span>\n\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Refrão]\r</span>\n\r\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G13\">G13</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/C\">D/C</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7(5-)\">Bm7(5-)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vem pros meus braços meu amor, meu acalanto\r</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/C\">D/C</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7(5-)\">Bm7(5-)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Leva esse pranto pra bem longe de nós dois\r</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/C\">D/C</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7(5-)\">Bm7(5-)</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não deixe nada pra depois, é a saudade que me diz\r</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M\">G7M</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D9-\">D9-</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que ainda é tempo pra viver feliz</span>\n",
